catalog.title: Topics in Develop Science
catalog.description: This seminar is a graduate-level overview of topics in developmental science. The broad goals of the seminar are to orient students to the field and place them on a strong trajectory for success as graduate students and beyond.
catalog.subject: Psychology

catalog.title: Seminar in Beh Neuroscience
catalog.description: This class will meet the requirements for the Behavioral Neuroscience program's qualifying exam. The format will be independent study, with three written exams, a grant proposal, and an oral exam. Students should register for the section listed under their mentor's name.
